Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
defInCheckMaskShifts(25.10)                        defInCheckMaskShifts(25.10)

Name
       defInCheckMaskShifts

Syntax
       defInCheckMaskShifts {on | off | bypass}

       Type: Enum

       Default: off

       Checks  conflicts  between  DEF COMPONENT MASKSHIFT and MACRO MASKSHIFT
       values with the LEF FIXEDMASK and LAYERMASKSHIFT values,  respectively,
       in the technology and MACRO sections. You can set the following values:

              * on:  When  the  variable is set as on, the the tool will check
                for the conflict. In case of a conflict, the tool will give an
                error and stop running.

              * off: When the variable is set as off, the tool will not  check
                for the conflict.

              * bypass: When the variable is set as bypass, the tool will give
                and error message and will continue running.

Related Information
              * restoreDesign

